son Associates; Oudshoorn, H.I., De Tuinders in Wateringen en De Lier: Bijdrage tot de Godsdienstgeografie van het Westland (The farmers in Wateringen and De Lier: Contribution to the religious geography of the Westland) (1957) PhD Thesis, , Utrecht University; Oudshoorn, H.I., De Sociale Structuur (The Social Structure) (1964) Van Crisis Tot Kracht (From Crisis to Strength), pp. 103-112. , W.H. Kemmers, Naaldwijk: Bond Westland; Pavitt, K., Sectoral patterns of technical change: Towards a taxonomy and a theory (1984) Research Policy, 13 (6), pp. 343-373; Plantenberg, P., (1987) 100 Jaar Veilingen In De Tuinbouw (100 Years of Auctions In Horticulture), , Central Bureau of Horticultural Auctions in the Netherlands/Association of Floricultural Auctions in the Netherlands; Poole, M.S., van de Ven, A.H., Towards a general theory of innovation processes (1989) Research on the management of innovation: The Minnesota studies, pp. 637-662. , ed. A.H. Van de Ven, H.L. Angle and M.S. Poole, New York: Harper & Row; Sanchez, R., Mahoney, J.T., Modularity, flexibility, and knowledge management in product and organization design (1996) Strategic Management Journal, 17 (1), pp. 63-76; Scholten, G., Sonneveld, C., Van langzaam herstel tot grote bloei, 1945-1965 (From slow recovery to rapid growth) (1999) Honderd Jaar Praktijkonderzoek Voor De Glastuinbouw (Hundred Years of Practical Research For Greenhouse Farming), pp. 21-35. , ed. J. Van Doesburg, Doetinchem: Elsevier; Scott, W.R., (1995) Institutions and Organizations, , Thousand Oaks, CA: Sage; Schumpeter, J.A., (1976) Capitalism, Socialism and Democracy, , London: George Allen & Unwin (originally published 1942); Simon, H.A., The organization of complex systems (1973) Hierarchy Theory: The Challenge of Complex Systems, pp. 1-27. , ed. H. Pattee, New York: George Braziller; Stender, J.A., De techniek in dienst van de glastuinbouw (Technology in the service of greenhouse farming) (1964) Va N Crisis Tot Kracht (From Crisis to Str