"Lachapelle A., Salomon J., Turinici G.","Computation of mean field equilibria in economics",2010,"Mathematical Models and Methods in Applied Sciences",20,4,,567,588,,4,"http://www.scopus.com/inward/record.url?eid=2-s2.0-77951911285&partnerID=40&md5=f08edfeb927123ace5f70664a3e2bb15","Ceremade UMR CNRS 7534, Université Paris-Dauphine, Place du Maréchal De Lattre De Tassigny, 75775 Paris Cedex 16, France","Lachapelle, A., Ceremade UMR CNRS 7534, Université Paris-Dauphine, Place du Maréchal De Lattre De Tassigny, 75775 Paris Cedex 16, France; Salomon, J., Ceremade UMR CNRS 7534, Université Paris-Dauphine, Place du Maréchal De Lattre De Tassigny, 75775 Paris Cedex 16, France; Turinici, G., Ceremade UMR CNRS 7534, Université Paris-Dauphine, Place du Maréchal De Lattre De Tassigny, 75775 Paris Cedex 16, France","Motivated by a mean field games stylized model for the choice of technologies (with externalities and economy of scale), we consider the associated optimization problem and prove an existence result. To complement the theoretical result, we introduce a monotonic algorithm to find the mean field equilibria. We close with some numerical results, including the multiplicity of equilibria describing the possibility of a technological transition. © 2010 World Scientific Publishing Company.","Dynamic equilibrium; Externalities; Mean field games; Monotonic algorithms; Non-convex optimization; Optimal control","Dynamic equilibria; Mean field; Monotonic algorithms; Nonconvex optimization; Optimal controls; Algorithms; Numerical analysis; Optimization; Convex optimization",,,,,,"Benamou, J.-D., Brenier, Y., A computational °uid mechanics solution to the Monge- Kantorovich mass transfer problem (2000) Numer. Math., 84, pp. 375-393; Buttazzo, G., Oudet, E., Jimenez, C., An optimization problem for mass transportation with congested dynamics (2008) Proc. of the 47th IEEE Conf. on Decision and Control, , http://cvgmt.sns.it/people/buttazzo/, preprint available at:, retrieved Sep